\begin_layout Subsection*
Guidelines for the choice of parameters
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The order of post-processing steps is user-specified.
 However, we recommend the following order: Remove duplicates (if MFA was
 enabled), filtering (to remove outliers), Z-stage offset (if applicable),
 drift correction, and finally merging.
\end_layout

